Process to consume external services or backing services

Manages configuration and credentials for back-end services while protecting sensitive data.

Makes service credentials available automatically as a secretes. 

Consumes the externeal by binding the application to a deployment. 

The app code uses the credentials from the binding and calls teh corresponding service. 

Service binding architecture. 

IBM CLOUD:

1. Provision an isntance of a servuce using IBM CLoud catalog
2. Bind service instance to your cluster
3: Verify secret stored in the cluster
4. Mount the secrete as a volume to your pod or reference the secret in environment variables. 
